              "name": "pg-dsm-test",
              "namespace": "monitoring",
              "notes": "1. Update values before first install:\n   - testProfile\n   - namespaceManagement\n   - postgres.host\n   - postgres.benchmarkDatabase\n   - postgres.pgbenchUser / postgres.pgbenchPassword\n\n2. Install or upgrade:\n   helm upgrade --install pg-dsm-test . -n monitoring --create-namespace\n\n3. This chart is addon-only:\n   - blackbox-exporter\n   - Probe resources\n   - Pushgateway\n   - Grafana dashboard ConfigMap\n   - pgbench runner and benchmark Jobs\n   - DSM DB cluster OS metrics collector\n\n4. Enable one test scenario at a time:\n   - jobs.init.enabled=true\n   - jobs.smoke.enabled=true\n   - jobs.baselineRw.enabled=true\n   - jobs.baselineRo.enabled=true\n   - jobs.ramp.enabled=true\n   - jobs.dataSweep10m.enabled=true\n   - jobs.dataSweep20m.enabled=true\n   - jobs.stress.enabled=true\n   - jobs.haObservation.enabled=true\n   - jobs.soak.enabled=true\n",
